{"tid":1231401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國台灣新聞都寫烈士失足墮下 唔係自殺","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:24.000Z","uid":60594,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"760bafc9064a4099322fe3d89e62c24da2f31033","tid":1231401,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAHbP1p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAHbP1p.png&h=64469dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aik8SeU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAik8SeU.png&h=ef8b1caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二張highlight左個句話有一名男子掛banner不小心失足墮下唔係自殺</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx7y3ni.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx7y3ni.png&h=c813aa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第三張圖<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong></strong></span></span>係話因為香港市民強烈反對只好暫緩條例<br />\n話62歲嘅林鄭月娥係有效率做實事嘅行政長官<br />\n佢嘅能力係廣泛網絡得到認同嘅特首</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家班韓國市民都屌緊總統點解唔出聲幫香港<br />\n因為依家總統係示威革命抗議朴槿惠下台佢先上到位<br />\n但因為韓國總統驚得罪中國一句聲都唔敢出</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d9727d07da3953157a03f13f9217a08d7e0a484","tid":1231401,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:50:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4853e9c51ba945ee40eb89e24e231f5dd96278e5","tid":1231401,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a480e99198a1e0f32a3870645ae50c3a8555c76a","tid":1231401,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fcc907b012788988d6715031a5e18d36713b2295","tid":1231401,"uid